data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Back to market with improvements.  Home qualifies as having an ADU.  This home is nestled within Bayshore Gardens Park and Recreation District, Bradenton, FL.  Bayshore Gardens offers its residents a wide range of social and recreational activities at its beautiful facilities on the shores of Sarasota Bay. Included amenities are the Jr. Olympic-size swimming pool, large pool deck/patio area, recreation hall, playground, picnic pavilions with BBQ grills, ball field, basketball courts and fishing pier with cleaning station. The marina offers a private/public boat ramp, annual boat dock rental (Subject to availability). In 2024 pickleball courts and a pool slide are to be added. Bradenton, FL is a charming city known for its beautiful beaches, vibrant arts scene and an array of parks, museums, restaurants, as well as home to IMG academy (IMG Academy is the world’s most esteemed sports, performance and educational institution).  This home is located in the Bayshore Gardens Park and Recreation District. NO HOA. It provides easy access to major highways convenient to reach nearby cities like Sarasota and Tampa. The home features many updates including: 2020 roof replacement, 2020 new insulation in attic, 2020 A/C change-out, a new garage door (2022), the main water line replaced in 2015, replacement of all interior doors, 2021, Aqua Water purification system, 2020, and most all windows have been replaced over the past 11 years.
